---
layout: base.njk
title: Writing
---

<div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
    <h1 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8">Writing</h1>
    
    <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-8">
        Explore Nick Dove's body of work, from published novels to short stories and essays.
    </p>

    <div class="space-y-8">
        <!-- Featured Work -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm p-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-6">Featured Work</h2>
            {% for work in writing %}
            <div>
                <p>{{ work.title }}</p>
                <p>{{ work.publishedBy }}
            </div>
            {% endfor %}
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
                <div class="border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">The Silent Echo</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
                        A contemporary novel exploring themes of memory, loss, and redemption. 
                        Set against the backdrop of a small coastal town, this story follows 
                        the journey of a man confronting his past.
                    </p>
                    <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
                        <span class="text-sm text-gray-500">Published 2023</span>
                        <span class="bg-green-100 text-green-800 text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded-full">Available</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Shadows of Tomorrow</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
                        A science fiction thriller that examines the consequences of technological 
                        advancement and human ambition. A thought-provoking exploration of 
                        what it means to be human.
                    </p>
                    <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
                        <span class="text-sm text-gray-500">Published 2022</span>
                        <span class="bg-green-100 text-green-800 text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded-full">Available</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Short Stories -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm p-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-6">Short Stories</h2>
            
            <div class="space-y-6">
                <div class="border-l-4 border-blue-500 pl-6">
                    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">The Last Letter</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">
                        A poignant story about a woman who discovers a letter from her late husband, 
                        leading her on a journey of self-discovery and healing.
                    </p>
                    <span class="text-sm text-gray-500">Published in Literary Review, 2023</span>
                </div>
                
                <div class="border-l-4 border-blue-500 pl-6">
                    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Coffee Shop Conversations</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">
                        A series of interconnected vignettes set in a local coffee shop, exploring 
                        the lives of regular customers and the barista who serves them.
                    </p>
                    <span class="text-sm text-gray-500">Published in Urban Tales, 2022</span>
                </div>
                
                <div class="border-l-4 border-blue-500 pl-6">
                    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">The Garden at Midnight</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">
                        A magical realism story about a gardener who discovers that his plants 
                        have the ability to reveal hidden truths about the people who tend them.
                    </p>
                    <span class="text-sm text-gray-500">Published in Fantasy Quarterly, 2021</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Essays -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm p-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-6">Essays & Articles</h2>
            
            <div class="space-y-6">
                <div class="border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6">
                    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">The Art of Slow Reading</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">
                        An exploration of how taking time to savor literature can deepen our 
                        understanding and appreciation of the written word.
                    </p>
                    <span class="text-sm text-gray-500">Published in The Reader's Journal, 2023</span>
                </div>
                
                <div class="border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6">
                    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Writing in the Digital Age</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">
                        Reflections on how technology has changed the way we write, read, and 
                        engage with literature in the 21st century.
                    </p>
                    <span class="text-sm text-gray-500">Published in Modern Literature, 2022</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Coming Soon -->
        <div class="bg-blue-50 rounded-lg p-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-blue-900 mb-4">Coming Soon</h2>
            <p class="text-blue-800 mb-4">
                Mike is currently working on his next novel, a historical fiction piece set 
                during the early 20th century. Stay tuned for updates and release information.
            </p>
            <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-4">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Work in Progress</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600">
                    "The Clockmaker's Daughter" - A story of family secrets, mechanical wonders, 
                    and the passage of time in a rapidly changing world.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div> 